            "text": "Integrating FLUX.1 schnell involves using its RESTful API with standard authentication (e.g., API keys) and JSON payloads. Compared to OpenAI, FLUX.1 schnell has a streamlined endpoint structure, reducing setup complexity. Ensure your system handles rate limits, retries, and error codes (e.g., 429 for rate limiting) effectively. Both APIs support common programming languages via SDKs, but FLUX.1 schnell's documentation emphasizes minimal dependencies."
