            "text": "Cost efficiency is paramount for scalable APIs. FLUX.1 schnell uses a token-based pricing model with no upfront fees, often resulting in lower costs for high-volume usage. Latency can be optimized through request batching, asynchronous processing, and caching strategies. Monitor usage dashboards to track expenses and avoid overages, especially during traffic spikes."
